query:
SELECT 
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM purchases WHERE areaId IS NULL AND isExcluded = 0) as unmatched,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM purchases WHERE areaId IS NOT NULL) as matched,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM purchases WHERE isExcluded = 1) as excluded,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM purchases) as total
